{"tid":1057854,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼市幾時開始一家親？","createTime":"2019-03-12T07:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T03:40:35.000Z","uid":3017,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf8923da62f3f0d44a0b8c3b74233c5bbc70562","tid":1057854,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"曼聯唔係應該好憎曼城？<br />\n費格遜時代統領英超，英超最多冠軍球隊<br />\n望住一隊暴發户，冇歷史既曼城<br />\n而家因為見到佢地領先緊垃圾利<br />\n所以曼聯幫曼城含撚，呢樣野可以點解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f2a26fddcf1e35e7f3bf304f6ba1aeb58a47b6","tid":1057854,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84655ef689da3ecf3e1b9e285caf6134dd838f","tid":1057854,"uid":169,"like":55,"dislike":8,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e20b5e64abe333af511507350bacc59fc27201d","tid":1057854,"uid":169,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a963f0e422fc915df0939923617924ebdb6dc585","tid":1057854,"uid":217509,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e79c44d8514143f4e4f23a0b5f4487832545b71","tid":1057854,"uid":14075,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"同市光榮思想掘起"},{"pid":"f1b735c29605719e7c6f90d68ce4bcb3918ea7e2","tid":1057854,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"1.曼市發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.哥迪奧拿同韓總一樣 都係光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a34e78fbaa35e41e68229a544772913a90772e9","tid":1057854,"uid":9931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"感情呢樣野唔係一條數 冇得計<br />\n<br />\n人地早排仲係到多謝高普"},{"pid":"1e400bd73f7d90781e68725ce30e56e8b0de23b3","tid":1057854,"uid":42246,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"早排有曼迷成日講：<br />\n垃圾車比曼市炒8-0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心諗曼聯都係2:0姐 講到自己大炒車咁（阿仙奴都2:0啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次見識到曼市一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9497b4c04c0ccb4cbff074bc6454108b20aecfd4","tid":1057854,"uid":80904,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"利申先 獌<br />\n我自己就反對同市光榮呢樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n鏝奪冠故知然難受<br />\n不過鏝猁奪冠二選一咁就梗係選鏝<br />\n話晒我獌最大嘅成就唔係贏咗幾多冠軍<br />\n係將猁喺霸主位置拉落凡間"},{"pid":"bf8a8d1a6dbbce8d0f8cf5ebacb7d3a6bf515b38","tid":1057854,"uid":218166,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"同市好榮論好似係猁狗講出黎先😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"3d483e4a67ca7a2b989ed435b25f7752c9039a83","tid":1057854,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"bf8a8d1a6dbbce8d0f8cf5ebacb7d3a6bf515b38","tid":1057854,"uid":218166,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"同市好榮論好似係猁狗講出黎先😂😂😂😂"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"又拉利狗落水？"},{"pid":"e541fce87359825a5cb6f21edddea25aa5f4e801","tid":1057854,"uid":2559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9497b4c04c0ccb4cbff074bc6454108b20aecfd4","tid":1057854,"uid":80904,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"利申先 獌<br />\n我自己就反對同市光榮呢樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n鏝奪冠故知然難受<br />\n不過鏝猁奪冠二選一咁就梗係選鏝<br />\n話晒我獌最大嘅成就唔係贏咗幾多冠軍<br />\n係將猁喺霸主位置拉落凡間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos